    "plan_content": "Here's a summary of the comprehensive plan I've created at `/Users/timpietrusky/.claude/plans/rustling-leaping-shamir.md`:\n\n---\n\n## Plan Summary: PulseBoard Channel Plugin\n\n**21 new files** in `extensions/pulseboard/` — no existing files modified.\n\n### PulseBoard-Specific Design\n- **Board targets**: `@board-name` (e.g. `@general`) — groups\n- **DM targets**: `username` (e.g. `alice`) — direct  \n- **Auth**: `apiUrl` + `apiKey` + `username` (env vars: `PULSEBOARD_API_URL`, `PULSEBOARD_API_KEY`, `PULSEBOARD_USERNAME`)\n- **Text chunk limit**: 4000 chars (with newline-respecting inline chunker in `send.ts`)\n- **Client**: stub implementation (fictional platform — no external npm deps)\n\n### File Structure\n```\nextensions/pulseboard/\n├── package.json                # no external deps, channel.id = \"pulseboard\"\n├── openclaw.plugin.json        # id: \"pulseboard\", channels: [\"pulseboard\"]\n├── index.ts / setup-entry.ts  # defineChannelPluginEntry / defineSetupPluginEntry\n├── api.ts / channel-config-api.ts\n└── src/\n    ├── runtime-api.ts          # internal barrel (imports from 7 public SDK paths)\n    ├── runtime.ts              # createPluginRuntimeStore\n    ├── types.ts                # CoreConfig, PulseBoardAccountConfig, etc.\n    ├── accounts.ts             # resolvePulseBoardAccount, listPulseBoardAccountIds\n    ├── config-schema.ts        # Zod schema + buildChannelConfigSchema\n    ├── config-ui-hints.ts      # UI hints\n    ├── normalize.ts            # isBoardTarget, normalizePulseBoardMessagingTarget\n    ├── policy.ts               # resolvePulseBoardGroupMatch\n    ├── send.ts                 # sendMessagePulseBoard + chunkPulseBoardText\n    ├── inbound.ts              # handlePulseBoardInbound\n    ├── monitor.ts              # monitorPulseBoardProvider (stub wait loop)\n    ├── probe.ts                # probePulseBoard (stub)\n    ├── setup-core.ts           # pulseBoardSetupAdapter\n    ├── setup-surface.ts        # pulseBoardSetupWizard\n    └── channel.ts              # createChatChannelPlugin (main plugin)\n```\n\n### Key Design Decision: No `openclaw/plugin-sdk/pulseboard` facade\nIRC's internal barrel re-exports from `openclaw/plugin-sdk/irc` (a dedicated facade). Since creating `src/plugin-sdk/pulseboard.ts` would modify existing files, the PulseBoard `src/runtime-api.ts` imports directly from 7 generic public SDK paths — all verified to be in `scripts/lib/plugin-sdk-entrypoints.json`.\n\n### Verification\n- `pnpm tsgo` — type check\n- `pnpm check` — lint  \n- `test/plugin-npm-release.test.ts` — manifest invariant\n- `test/plugin-extension-import-boundary.test.ts` — boundary check\n- Workspace auto-picks up `extensions/pulseboard/` via `extensions/*` glob — no changes to `pnpm-workspace.yaml` needed",
